"Warning! Warning!" I hear the voice of the Overseer, whose green-eyed drone was apparently still following me. "The Overseer protocol is detecting aura manipulation techniques dangerously close to this unit's coordinates. If you do not stop immediately, this unit will be forced to call for backup."

"Overseer, you were ordered to retreat," the captain says. "Leave this area now, or you will face the consequences."

"Error!" the Overseer says. "Cannot comply with that order!"

