"You're telling me to get even closer to those murderers while you're not there to protect me?!" the ambassador says. "What if they kill me?"

"They're not going to kill you," the captain says. "They are all being immobilized, and I will make a small mobile barrier between you and them to protect you as you walk, just in case. Now please go to your shelter. Even I can't hold them like this forever."

